# Annual Captures
### Spring Surveys
```{r 4. Fish Captures - Summary Table catch_dat.prep, echo=FALSE, warning=FALSE, message = FALSE, include = FALSE}
source("SourceFiles/4. Annual Captures.R")
```


Since 2008, a total of `r format(sum(catch_annual.Table.Spring$nCT), big.mark =",")` juvenile Coastal Cutthroat Trout and `r format(sum(catch_annual.Table.Spring$nCO), big.mark =",")` juvenile Coho Salmon have been captured during spring trapping. Annual captures of CCT and CO have ranged from `r format(min(catch_annual.Table.Spring$nCT), big.mark =",")` to `r format(max(catch_annual.Table.Spring$nCT), big.mark =",")` and `r format(min(catch_annual.Table.Spring$nCO), big.mark =",")` to `r format(max(catch_annual.Table.Spring$nCO), big.mark =",")`, respectively, with overall means of `r format(mean(catch_annual.Table.Spring$nCT), digits = 1)` CCT and `r format(mean(catch_annual.Table.Spring$nCO), digits = 1)` CO.

